- # Student-facing launch view inside the Canvas iframe once they're
- # enrolled: the header confirms the connection, with the course title
- # linking out to the Dashboard course in a new tab. Rendered instead of
- # redirecting to the course page — the full dashboard can't render inside
- # the iframe (Firefox enforces the course page's X-Frame-Options outright,
- # and the React shell reads logged-out under partitioned cookies
- # elsewhere). Top-level launches still redirect.
.lti-iframe__drilldown
  = render 'lti_launch/drilldown_header',
           title: t('lti.status.header'), course: @binding.course, linked_check: true
